      <h3>Guidance Request Resource</h3>
      <p>Represents a pending guidance request requiring European Commission clarification. Links to related FAQs that provide temporary solutions or context.</p>

      <h4>Attributes</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><code>title</code> - The guidance request title in markdown format</li>
        <li><code>titleHtml</code> - The title rendered as HTML</li>
        <li><code>body</code> - The guidance request details in markdown</li>
        <li><code>bodyHtml</code> - The body rendered as HTML</li>
        <li><code>guidanceText</code> - Plain text summary of guidance needed</li>
        <li><code>status</code> - Status of the guidance request (e.g., pending)</li>
        <li><code>createdAt</code> - ISO 8601 timestamp of creation</li>
        <li><code>lastUpdatedAt</code> - ISO 8601 timestamp of last update</li>
        <li><code>author</code> - Content author attribution</li>
        <li><code>authorUrl</code> - URL to author/contributor page</li>
        <li><code>license</code> - License designation (CC BY 4.0)</li>
        <li><code>licenseUrl</code> - URL to license terms</li>
        <li><code>srcUrl</code> - Link to source in GitHub repository</li>
        <li><code>editOnGithubUrl</code> - Direct edit link to GitHub</li>
      </ul>

      <h4>Relationships</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><code>relatedFaqs</code> - Array of FAQ resources that provide context or temporary solutions</li>
      </ul>

